tonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wdj1665702655632.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wdj1665702655632.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wdj1665702655632.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wdj1665702655632\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /dev\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Compile device translation tables.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__section_w2229ab1b5b1_w2230ab1b5_w2231ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__p_d148730e1_d148731e1_d148732e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/dev</span> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inf</span>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__section_w2232ab1b5b3_w2233ab1b5_w2234ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d95844e85\">\n                  \n Switches\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__li_d51656e1_d51657e1_d51658e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ide1665702625805.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ide1665702625805.html\" title=\"Compile objects modified after and/or before the date specified.\">/aft= or /bef=</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__li_d51659e1_d51660e1_d51661e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"czj1665702653450.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/czj1665702653450.html\" title=\"Display the information listing plus warning and error messages when compiling.\">/inf</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__section_w2235ab1b5b5_w2236ab1b5_w2237ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d95844e114\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__p_d148739e1_d148740e1_d148741e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>—name of the library containing the objects to compile; if omitted, all device and printer translation tables are compiled. You can use wildcard characters to specify a group of libraries.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__section_w2238ab1b5b7_w2239ab1b5_w2240ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d95844e126\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__d5931e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.exe</span>—Uniface IDE</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__section_w2241ab1b5b9_w2242ab1b5_w2243ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d95844e138\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wdj1665702655632__p_d148751e1_d148752e1_d148753e1\">The location of compiled tables is determined by the $RSO path.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfc1665702625593.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Compiling from the IDE Command Line</a><p>The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ejp1665702655701.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Device Translation Tables</a><p>Device translation tables handle output to screens and printers. They map Uniface logical functions onto device functions, making it possible for Uniface to support a wide variety of hardware platforms, including their output devices.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533310\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533310\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/dev Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /dev Compile device translation tables. /dev { /aft = DateTime } { /bef = DateTime } { /inf } { Library } Switches /aft= or /bef= /inf Parameters Library —name of the library containing the objects to compile; if omitted, all device and printer translation tables are compiled. You can use wildcard characters to specify a group of libraries. Use With ide.exe —Uniface IDE Description The location of compiled tables is determined by the $RSO path. Related Links Compiling from the IDE Command Line The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts. Device Translation Tables Device translation tables handle output to screens and printers. They map Uniface logical functions onto device functions, making it possible for Uniface to support a wide variety of hardware platforms, including their output devices. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}